&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/EUR-PORTUGAL-VILA-JOYA-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4457&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/EUR-PORTUGAL-VILA-JOYA-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;EUR- PORTUGAL- VILA JOYA- OFFER- LOGO MEDIUM&quot; width=&quot;75&quot; height=&quot;71&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.theworlds50best.com/list/1-50-winners/vila-joya&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-3444&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/W50B-LOGO-SMALL.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;50Best_2014_logo&quot; width=&quot;50&quot; height=&quot;87&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Combining local fish and produce with imported products, Austrian-born chef &lt;strong&gt;Dieter Koschina&lt;/strong&gt; creates innovative cuisine that delights the senses. Considered the finest restaurant in Portugal, Vila Joya Restaurant has earned &lt;strong&gt;2 Michelin stars&lt;/strong&gt; and is &lt;strong&gt;World&amp;#8217;s 50 Best Restaurants #98 for 2015&lt;/strong&gt;. Whether indoors or on the terrace, you&rsquo;ll dine with a view of the lush Algarve coastline. Casual elegant attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book online contacting Vila Joya by phone at +351-28-59-795, by email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@vilajoya.com&quot;&gt;info@vilajoya.com&lt;/a&gt; or on the Vila Joya online submission form on their &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.vilajoya.com/en/cuisine/2-michelin-star-restaurant/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;website&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Booking Requirements &ndash; A valid credit card is required for booking. Your reservation is not valid until Vila Joya confirms to you via email&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy &ndash; As a courtesy Vila Joya asks for 24 hour cancellation cancelled within 24 hours notice. A fee of 60 Euro per person will be charged to the credit card on file if not&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must use your Diners Club Card for payment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection Amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vila Joya serves a fixed menu there are no exceptions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preferred bookings and upgrade to chef&rsquo;s table are based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offer available at dinner only&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

